```{r}
library(RJSONIO)
library(data.table)

json_file <- fromJSON("session_2021-07-10_19-14-39_A30.json")


obj1 <- lapply(json_file$objectives[[1]]$data, function(x) {
  x[sapply(x, is.null)] <- NA
  unlist(x)
})

df<-as.data.frame(do.call("cbind", obj1))
```

```{r}

dft = transpose(df)
colnames(dft) = rownames(df)
#rownames(dft) = colnames(df)
```
